title: G-box Key
description:
Program your G-Box Midnight MX2 with the latest and greatest add-ons in under three minutes flat.
Simply plug our G-Box Key into your G-Box, then press a few buttons, and you are done.
We include a video tutorial with the G-Box Key that will show you how to use it.
After you have followed our simple video instructions, your G-Box will have over 100 working add-ons.
Here is a small sample of included addons: 1channel, Icefilms, Crackle, Adult Entertainment, Sportsdevil, TMZ, MASHUP, NBA Video, Fast Pass Tv, Veetle, Vevo, Pandora, Youtube, Funny or Die, America's Test Kitchen, DIY Network, Vimeo and many more.
